<li><i>Creation, Law and Probability</i> (Fortress Press 2008) ed <a href="/wiki/Fraser_Watts" title="Fraser Watts">Fraser Watts</a>) with <a href="/wiki/Peter_Harrison" title="Peter Harrison">Peter Harrison</a>, <a href="/wiki/George_Ellis" title="George Ellis">George Ellis</a>, <a href="/wiki/Philip_Clayton" title="Philip Clayton">Philip Clayton</a>, <a href="/wiki/Michael_Ruse" title="Michael Ruse">Michael Ruse</a>, <a href="/wiki/Nancey_Murphy" title="Nancey Murphy">Nancey Murphy</a>, <a href="/wiki/John_Bowker" title="John Bowker">John Bowker</a> &amp; others <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780800662783" class="internal">ISBN 978-0800662783</a></li>
</ul>
